data.description: Priced to sell! This spacious 2-story offers many delightful features including 2 living areas. Chef's dream kitchen with abundant counter space, center island and large, walk-in pantry for organization. Cozy up in the reading nook while enjoying the gas fireplace or escape to the versatile living space upstairs with an additional kitchen, office space, and views from your private deck. Sip your coffee from your balcony or the patio in your secluded backyard. Property comes complete with a generously sized workshop, automatic sprinklers, and backyard access for easy yard maintenance. This property provides the perfect balance of comfortable country living and city accessibility, just a short drive from Albuquerque. Call this one yours just in time for the holidays.
